Available Tools: get_prescriptions | request_refill | check_drug_interaction | get_medication_info
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "patient_id": "string", "medication": "string", "dosage": "string" }
Response Schema: { "prescription_id": "string", "medication": "string", "dosage": "string", "refills_remaining": number, "status": "string" }
---
Question: Show me the prescription record for patient P72819 concerning their amoxicillin 500mg.
Call: { "func_call": "get_prescriptions", "patient_id": "P72819", "medication": "amoxicillin", "dosage": "500mg" }
Response: { "prescription_id": "RX-2024-9021", "medication": "amoxicillin", "dosage": "500mg", "refills_remaining": 0, "status": "completed" }

